# APISignalTrack - API Uptime & Delay Monitor

APISignalTrack scans endpoint signals and gives a clear view of system health across services.

## Features
- Latency + status monitoring  
- CSV or JSON reporting  
- Threshold alerts  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/27_APISignalTrack.git
cd 27_APISignalTrack
python monitor.py
